name: Jaina Solo
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. X-Wings deploy -1 (and are immune to attrition < 5) here. During your control phase, may tkae one non-unique X-Wing (or Rogue Squadron pilot) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Adds one battle destiny with a Skywalker or another Solo. Immune to attrition < 4 (< 6 if with Leia).',
